Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI.utils

Enum Class Colors

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Colors>
it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI.utils.Colors
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Colors>, Constable
public enum Colors extends Enum<Colors>
Enumeration Colors provide all the constants of the unicode standard that are used for changing color to text character. Each constant have the corresponding unicode value associated.
